column5: I'm trying to open the post called "Power Trip" and just keep getting this message.   "An Error Occurred Sorry, an error occurred. If you are unsure on how to use a feature, or don't know why you got this error message, try looking through the help files for more information.  [#10342] We could not determine which forum this topic is in."
Well, it was there a couple minutes ago
thats because there were no mods on for a bit...
Jeeez, there's so many post getting locked, deleted or edited lately, it's hard to keep up with everything.

It was a video of a homeless guy being beated to death by some cops in California.  Not suited for OFC.  I understand the intent of the post, but the content of the video was over the top for a site like OFC.  You didn't miss anything Lew.  But if you have an itching to find out more.  The guys name was Kelly Thomas.  The cops are being charged, one with murder.
Thanks Nick, but it sounds like something I'd rather not see anyways.
